Position overview:
Tencent’s Global Communications department is seeking a bright, creative, digital-savvy writer and storyteller to inject fresh, new ideas into our communications team and help us grow Tencent as a leading global internet and technology company.
The right candidate will be joining an international team that’s highly focused on enhancing Tencent’s brand reputation and engagement globally. He or she will play a proactive role in identifying potential stories within Tencent and developing content for media, the website, social channels, news releases, and more.

What you will be doing:
Be immersed in Tencent’s businesses, learning about products, services, projects and technologies that will help power our content calendar and relations with international media;
Use excellent judgment to identify potential news or social media updates;
Write compelling content in English and Chinese across different platforms, with an ability to understand tone of voice and use it appropriately;
Be proactive in suggesting new methods, content, or ways of doing things to improve efficiency and further enhance the quality of our content;
Liaise regularly with journalists and develop clear, factual responses to media enquiries;
Build strong relationships both inside Tencent and externally with media and other stakeholders;

